title: Create the schwifty chain
description: This corrects  the issues found in prop-8. This is a new proposal (prop-9) to create the consumer chain "schwifty-1". Visit https://github.com/toschdev/ics-testnets/tree/main/game-of-chains-2022/schwifty/prop-9/ for details on this proposal's data and how to join the chain.
